xsTPTIRC is an IRC client for The Powder Toy (http://powdertoy.co.uk)
After loading the script, press Ctrl+M to open/hide window
Ctrl+Shift+M will terminate the client.
To join a channel type 
 /join #channel
To leave a channel type
 /part #channel
To open a PM with someone type
 /open nickname
To close PM type
 /close nickname
To clear text in window type
 /clear windowname

On first run client will create a configuration file,
in which you can edit your default nick, server and port,
also you can edit channels to be automatically joined upon connection.

P.S: yeah, client misses lots of features, i know. Just wait some time and ill add them.